title: Mobile
description: Mobile typically refers to devices, services, or technologies that are designed for use while on the move, such as smartphones, tablets, and mobile applications.

title: Shoes
description: shoes are a type of footwear worn on the feet to provide protection, support, and comfort while walking or performing various activities.

title: shirt
description: A shirt is a piece of clothing typically made of fabric that covers the upper body.

title: Formal one piece
description: A one-piece dress is a single garment that combines a top and a skirt or bottom into a single piece, typically designed to be worn as a dress. It's a one-stop outfit that doesn't require matching separate pieces like a top and a bottom.

title: Belt
description: A belt is a flexible band or strap typically made of leather or fabric that is worn around the waist to hold clothing in place, cinch garments for a better fit, or as a fashion accessory.

title: Oven
description: An oven is a kitchen appliance used for baking, roasting, or heating food by surrounding it with dry, hot air. It typically has a compartment with adjustable temperature controls for cooking a wide range of dishes.

title: Bulb
description: A bulb is a device that produces light when an electric current passes through a filament or gas inside a glass or plastic enclosure. It's a common source of artificial lighting in homes and various other settings.
